Package: mvPred
Type: Package
Title: Methods for Handling Missing Values in Linear Modeling
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Norman", "Matloff", email = "nsmatloff@ucdavis.edu", role = "aut"),
    person("Cynthia", "Mascarenhas", email = "cin22jan@gmail.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Billy", "Ouattara", email = "ouattarabilly33@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Alekya", "Veluri", email = "alekyaveluri@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Maintainer: Billy Ouattara <ouattarabilly33@hotmail.com>
Description: Provides user-friendly methods for handling missing data in regression modeling, including available-case linear regression, multiple imputation using mice, Amelia, and missForest, and missing-data handling via the toweranNA package.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports:
